<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22Aug1936"><font color="red">22 August 1936</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver): Mr and Mrs Joyce left Paris Tuesday last (18 August 1936) for Copenhagen as their ultimate destination &hellip; Mrs Jolas &hellip; could not come near the Joyce&apos;s flat for all the time she was in Paris &hellip; The Gilberts have not been at the Joyces for now nearly eighteen months. </div>
